Metadata: Two new alkaloids from an Indian species of "Zoanthus"

A new species of "Zoanthus" from the Bay of Bengal contains a novel group of alkaloids that possess anti-​inflammatory and analgesic properties. The structures of two new isomeric alkaloids, 28-​deoxyzoanthenam​ine and 22-​epi-​28-​deoxyzoanthenam​ine, were elucidated by interpretation of spectral data and are reported here.
